<subSubSection pageId="6" pageNumber="55" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="6.[151,1437,338,604]" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[198,319,378,404]" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">Remarks.</emphasis>
This species looks similar externally to the figures of 
<taxonomicName authority="Vilbaste (1968)" authorityName="Vilbaste" authorityYear="1968" box="[955,1372,378,404]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Scaphoideus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="varius">
<emphasis box="[955,1183,378,403]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">Scaphoideus varius</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation author="Vilbaste, J." box="[1190,1372,378,404]" pageId="6" pageNumber="55" refId="ref3117" refString="Vilbaste, J. (1968) Uber die Zicadenfauna des Primorje Gebietes. Tallinn 180 pp. 14 pls." type="book" year="1968">Vilbaste (1968)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[151,232,418,444]" name="Russia" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">Russia</collectingCountry>
, given by 
<bibRefCitation author="Lee, C. E." box="[353,486,418,444]" pageId="6" pageNumber="55" refId="ref2959" refString="Lee, C. E. (1979) Illustrated flora and fauna of Korea. Vol. 23 Insecta (VII), 1070 pp. Ministry of Education." type="book" year="1979">Lee (1979)</bibRefCitation>
, of which the line drawing habitus figure was originally produced in the description of 
<taxonomicName authority="Kwon &amp; Lee" authorityName="Kwon &amp; Lee" authorityYear="1978" box="[238,579,458,484]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Scaphoideus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hongdoensis">
<emphasis box="[238,253,458,483]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[268,414,458,483]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">hongdoensis</emphasis>
Kwon &amp; Lee
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry box="[653,728,458,484]" name="South Korea" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">Korea</collectingCountry>
. Presumably therefore, the un-stated synonymy of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Vilbaste" authorityYear="1968" box="[1332,1436,458,484]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Scaphoideus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="varius">
<emphasis box="[1332,1347,458,483]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[1363,1436,458,483]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">varius</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Kwon &amp; Lee" authorityYear="1978" box="[200,375,498,524]" class="Insecta" family="Cicadellidae" genus="Scaphoideus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hemiptera" pageId="6" pageNumber="55" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="hongdoensis">
<emphasis box="[200,215,498,523]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">S</emphasis>
. 
<emphasis box="[229,375,498,523]" italics="true" pageId="6" pageNumber="55">hongdoensis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
in 
<bibRefCitation author="Lee, C. E." box="[412,541,498,524]" pageId="6" pageNumber="55" refId="ref2959" refString="Lee, C. E. (1979) Illustrated flora and fauna of Korea. Vol. 23 Insecta (VII), 1070 pp. Ministry of Education." type="book" year="1979">Lee (1979)</bibRefCitation>
dates from that publication. Both sets of male genitalia figures are the same. Strangely, none of the references in 
<bibRefCitation author="Kwon, Y. J. &amp; Lee, C. E." box="[569,805,538,564]" pageId="6" pageNumber="55" pagination="21 - 24" refId="ref2913" refString="Kwon, Y. J. &amp; Lee, C. E. (1978) A new species of Scaphoideus Uhler from Is. Hongdo, Korea (Homoptera: Auchenorrhyncha). The Korean Journal of Entomology, 8, 21 - 24." type="journal article" year="1978">Kwon &amp; Lee’s 1978</bibRefCitation>
paper (including Vilbaste’s) appear in the text of their paper, suggesting perhaps that the paper was extracted from a larger work.
</paragraph>
